message.entry: An empty cell array is not a valid input argument.
QUIVER does not support {0} leading numeric input(s).
Scale argument must be a scalar double or 'off'.
U and V must be the same size.
X,Y both must be empty or both nonempty.
The size of X must match the size of U or the number of columns of U.
The size of Y must match the size of U or the number of rows of U.
Z and U must be the same size.
V and W must be the same size.
The size of X must match the size of Z or the number of columns of Z.
The size of Y must match the size of Z or the number of rows of Z.
The sizes of X and Y must match the size of Z, or X and Y must be vectors whose lengths match the number of columns and rows, respectively, of Z.
The sizes of X and Y must match the size of U, or X and Y must be vectors whose lengths match the number of columns and rows, respectively, of U.
